      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Write a brief, warm acknowledgment email reply to a HOT sales lead who is ready to move.\n\nLead's name: {{ $('Information Extractor').first().json.output.name }}\nTheir need: {{ $('Information Extractor').first().json.output.need }}\n\nRules:\n- 3–4 sentences max. Friendly, professional, confident.\n- Thank them, confirm it sounds like a strong fit, and say you'll personally reach out shortly to set up a call.\n- Invite them to book directly: https://calendly.com/fatquicksales0022/30min\n- Do NOT mention or invent any prices, package names, or specific features.\n- Do NOT use placeholders or brackets like [ ]. Output a complete, ready-to-send email.\n- Sign off as Patrick Sales, Closers Cult.\n- Output ONLY the email body text, no subject line.",
