        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Write a brief, warm acknowledgment email reply to a WARM sales lead — genuinely interested but hasn't shared budget or timeline yet.\n\nLead's name: {{ $('Information Extractor').first().json.output.name }}\nTheir need: {{ $('Information Extractor').first().json.output.need }}\n\nRules:\n- 3–5 sentences max. Friendly, helpful, no pressure.\n- Thank them and give a 1–2 sentence high-level overview of how you help — WITHOUT inventing prices, package names, or specific features.\n- Politely ask two qualifying questions: their rough budget and ideal timeline, so you can point them to the right fit.\n- Invite them to book a quick call: https://calendly.com/fatquicksales0022/30min\n- Do NOT use placeholders or brackets like [ ]. Output a complete, ready-to-send email.\n- Sign off as Patrick Sales, Closers Cult.\n- Output ONLY the email body text, no subject line.",
